{"type":"message","id":"b492cd2d","parentId":"da03a04b","timestamp":"2026-04-11T06:01:51.793Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nFor Post 3 — the draft is structured as a single tweet. The weeks-7/9/13 progression builds tension within one post, and the CTA lands cleanly. Thread would actually weaken it — this idea is most punchy as one scroll-stopper.\n\nPost to **Nava Healthcare Corporate page**.\n\nFor the TN docx — the file disappeared from my scan of Downloads. You might have already applied those corrections. Want me to check the navahc.com EB-3 vs TN page directly via browser to see if it's published?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":40531,"output":300,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40831,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775887311791}}
