{"type":"message","id":"2a36378c","parentId":"29e94521","timestamp":"2026-04-11T06:55:42.022Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-11 08:36:10 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:36:15 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:37:15 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:37:20 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected as +27763674298.\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:38:20 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:38:26 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:39:26 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:39:31 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:40:31 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:40:35 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:41:35 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:41:40 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:42:40 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:42:45 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:43:45 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:43:50 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:44:50 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:44:56 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:45:56 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway disconnected (status 499)\nSystem: [2026-04-11 08:46:01 GMT+2] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-11 08:55 GMT+2] I added surpirsingly because I think it is common knowledge/belief that breaking contracts like the NC or NDA has dire consequences - probably due to TV