{"type":"message","id":"24c62c81","parentId":"fa7bee3f","timestamp":"2026-04-11T07:35:43.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nDone. Editor skill updated with 6 new real-time principles and the memory notes file expanded with Round 2 details. Both committed.\n\nNow — back to the article. P3 when you're ready. I noticed you asked about H2/H3 structure — the current NC article uses flat H2 structure (no H3 nesting). Is that what you wanted to flag, or were you referring to something else?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":67150,"output":97,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67247,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775892943359}}
{"type":"message","id":"1d5738e0","parentId":"24c62c81","timestamp":"2026-04-11T07:37:30.016Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-11 09:37 GMT+2] I can fucking see that there are no H3s nested. I can't believe I'm fucking doing this everyday now. Go back and read the transcripts from last night and see what we discussed. Don't do anything, just read and report what you read."}],"timestamp":1775893050002}}
