{"type":"message","id":"cef78359","parentId":"4abc2845","timestamp":"2026-04-11T08:10:41.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nDone. Anti-bullshit guardrails committed (bd070a5), outline in memory, all in one place.\n\n**Where we are:**\n- NC article: current file has flat H2s, needs full rebuild to the approved 4×H2 / 12×H3 structure\n- Post 2 article (how to fire IC): also flat H2s, same issue\n- Both articles need AWAA to run phases against the approved outline — not a direct draft\n\n**The workflow going forward:**\n1. I read the skill SKILL.md before using a skill\n2. I read the agent system prompt before spawning agents  \n3. Phase workflow enforced: outline → H2 structure → H3 ideas → draft\n4. Structural audit before presenting to you\n\nReady to rebuild AWAA properly when you are. Do you want to start there, or finish the line-by-line on the NC article first?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":51081,"output":210,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51291,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775895041359}}
