{"type":"message","id":"4048206e","parentId":"c90d88b3","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:11:33.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\nNo. The draft is missing H3 structure.\n\nHere's the actual breakdown:\n\n**What canvas specified:**\n- H2.1 — 3 H3s (1.1.1, 1.1.2, 1.1.3), 6 paragraphs total\n- H2.2 — 3 H3s (2.2.1, 2.2.2, 2.2.3), 6 paragraphs total\n- H2.3 — 3 H3s (3.3.1, 3.3.2, 3.3.3), 6 paragraphs total\n- H2.4 — 2 H3s (4.4.1, 4.4.2), 4 paragraphs total\n\n**What the draft actually has:**\n- H2.1 — 2 paragraphs (H3.1.1 merged with H3.1.3, H3.1.2 missing entirely)\n- H2.2 — 5 paragraphs (but no H3 breaks, just continuous prose)\n- H2.3 — 5 paragraphs (same)\n- H2.4 — 4 paragraphs (same)\n\nThe H3s were supposed to be structural anchors in the final draft, not just canvas planning notes. AWAA wrote continuous prose and dropped the H3 headings.\n\nOptions:\n1. **Add H3 subheadings to the existing prose** — I can insert the H3 headings into the draft to match the canvas structure\n2. **Send AWAA back** — it should regenerate with explicit H3 subheadings\n3. **Keep as-is** — continuous prose without H3 breaks (more readable, less structured)\n\nWhich do you want?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":70857,"output":1206,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72063,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775898693018}}
