{"type":"message","id":"64469a1d","parentId":"e165d2bd","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:38:08.429Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_56b029f3-3b69-48a9-905a-19778b5eaba3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"On branch master\nChanges to be committed:\n  (use \"git restore --staged <file>...\" to unstage)\n\tnew file:   skills/drafting-skill/SKILL.md\n\tnew file:   skills/transitions-skill/SKILL.md\n\tnew file:   skills/transitions-skill/references/transition-examples.md\n\nChanges not staged for commit:\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to update what will be committed)\n  (use \"git restore <file>...\" to discard changes in working directory)\n\tmodified:   abroadworks/article-independent-contractor-non-compete.md\n\tmodified:   memory/2026-04-11.md\n\tmodified:   skills/abroadworks-writing/awaa-system-prompt.md\n\nUntracked files:\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to include in what will be committed)\n\tawaa-output/"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":323,"aggregated":"On branch master\nChanges to be committed:\n  (use \"git restore --staged <file>...\" to unstage)\n\tnew file:   skills/drafting-skill/SKILL.md\n\tnew file:   skills/transitions-skill/SKILL.md\n\tnew file:   skills/transitions-skill/references/transition-examples.md\n\nChanges not staged for commit:\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to update what will be committed)\n  (use \"git restore <file>...\" to discard changes in working directory)\n\tmodified:   abroadworks/article-independent-contractor-non-compete.md\n\tmodified:   memory/2026-04-11.md\n\tmodified:   skills/abroadworks-writing/awaa-system-prompt.md\n\nUntracked files:\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to include in what will be committed)\n\tawaa-output/","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775900288423}}
{"type":"message","id":"492c46b7","parentId":"64469a1d","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:38:19.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_5f867af8-3773-4d75-9e54-5fc4182b75d3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace && git commit -m \"Add drafting-skill and transitions-skill\n\ndrafting-skill — 4-step canvas-to-prose method:\n1. Convert paragraph ideas to full prose (leave headings/intros/FAQs/conclusion alone)\n2. Revise H2 intros to match section content\n3. Check transitions using transitions-skill\n4. Check FAQs against article argument\n\ntransitions-skill — logical thread methodology:\n- Level 1: vocabulary bridge (no same word family at boundaries)\n- Level 2: logical thread (last sentence of P1 sets up P2)\n- Level 3: argument escalation (P1 raises stakes, P2 resolves/escalates)\n- Pivot sentence rule: close implicates reader agency\n\nreferences/transition-examples.md — annotated good/bad examples\""}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":44804,"output":212,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45016,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775900299502}}
{"type":"message","id":"b1c40592","parentId":"492c46b7","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:38:19.591Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_5f867af8-3773-4d75-9e54-5fc4182b75d3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[master f58bd0f] Add drafting-skill and transitions-skill\n 3 files changed, 378 insertions(+)\n create mode 100644 skills/drafting-skill/SKILL.md\n create mode 100644 skills/transitions-skill/SKILL.md\n create mode 100644 skills/transitions-skill/references/transition-examples.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":74,"aggregated":"[master f58bd0f] Add drafting-skill and transitions-skill\n 3 files changed, 378 insertions(+)\n create mode 100644 skills/drafting-skill/SKILL.md\n create mode 100644 skills/transitions-skill/SKILL.md\n create mode 100644 skills/transitions-skill/references/transition-examples.md","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775900299585}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed6ea3c4","parentId":"b1c40592","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:38:26.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNow let me update `phased-outlining` to reference `drafting-skill` for Phase 5, so the full workflow is documented end-to-end:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_2960dd40-bfc1-4480-adbf-12ed72dbc3aa","name":"edit","arguments":{"new_string":"**Phases:**\n1. H1 approval\n2. H2 structure proposal\n3. H3 sub-headings with main ideas\n4. Paragraph canvas (main idea + logical flow per paragraph)\n5. Full draft prose — **see `drafting-skill` for the Phase 5 method**\n\n**Phase 5 is not part of this methodology.** This skill documents Phases 1-4 only. For Phase 5 execution, use the `drafting-skill`.","old_string":"**Phases:**\n1. H1 approval\n2. H2 structure proposal\n3. H3 sub-headings with main ideas\n4. Paragraph canvas (main idea + logical flow per paragraph)\n5. Full draft","path":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/phased-outlining/SKILL.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":45097,"output":296,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45393,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775900306857}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f87ac43","parentId":"ed6ea3c4","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:38:26.889Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_2960dd40-bfc1-4480-adbf-12ed72dbc3aa","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/phased-outlining/SKILL.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/phased-outlining/SKILL.md. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines."},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775900306881}}
{"type":"message","id":"90791f07","parentId":"7f87ac43","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:38:28.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_881b8ba6-d1bc-4dfa-8408-a3f4e62cc81f","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"path":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/phased-outlining/SKILL.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":45423,"output":67,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45490,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775900308963}}
{"type":"message","id":"74164143","parentId":"90791f07","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:38:28.983Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_881b8ba6-d1bc-4dfa-8408-a3f4e62cc81f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: phased-outlining\ndescription: Use when asked to plan, outline, or architect a long-form article, blog post, or content piece. Triggers on \"outline an article\", \"plan content\", \"build a structure\", \"create a canvas\", \"article architecture\", \"content scaffolding\". This skill covers Phases 1-4 only: H1 approval, H2 structure, H3 sub-headings, and paragraph canvas. Phase 5 (draft prose) is not part of this methodology and is not taught here.\n---\n\n# Phased Outlining — Article Architecture Methodology\n\nA strict multi-phase workflow for building a long-form article or blog post. Each phase gates the next. The writer does not move to prose until the editor approves the structure through Phase 4.\n\n**The four phases:**\n1. H1 approval\n2. H2 structure proposal\n3. H3 sub-headings with main ideas\n4. Paragraph canvas (main idea + logical flow per paragraph)\n\n**Phase 5 (draft prose) is not part of this methodology.**\n\n---\n\n## The Four Phases\n\n[130 more lines in file. Use offset=21 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775900308976}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7019fea","parentId":"74164143","timestamp":"2026-04-11T09:38:45.144Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGood — `phased-outlining` already says Phase 5 is not in scope. Skills are correctly scoped.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_9011c0cc-6434-4a8c-8b3b-17e9b6612402","name":"edit","arguments":{"new_string":"## Skills Added — Apr 11\n\n| Skill | Location | Description |\n|-------|----------|-------------|\n| `phased-outlining` | workspace skills | Article architecture methodology. Phases 1-4 only (H1→H2→H3→canvas). Phase 5 not included. |\n| `drafting-skill` | workspace skills | 4-step canvas-to-prose conversion: convert ideas→prose, revise H2 intros, check transitions, check FAQs |\n| `transitions-skill` | workspace skills | Logical thread method: vocabulary bridge, logical thread, argument escalation, pivot sentences |\n| `ai-humanizer` | workspace skills | Humanize AI-generated text — already existed |\n\n## Drafting Skill — Core Method (Apr 11)\n\nTiny taught the Phase 5 execution process:\n\n1. **Convert paragraph ideas to full prose** — AWAA follows canvas logical flow sentence-by-sentence. Don't touch headings, intros, FAQ, or conclusion.\n2. **Revise H2 intros** — make sure they represent what's actually discussed in the section\n3. **Check transitions** — use transitions-skill (logical thread between paragraphs, not just adding transition words)\n4. **Check FAQs** — questions must be derivable from the article's actual argument\n\n**Key principle:** The canvas logical flow = literal marching orders. Each sentence in the flow becomes a sentence in the prose.\n\n## Editor Skill Update — H2/H3 Structure (pending — explicitly requested by Tiny)","old_string":"## Editor Skill Update — H2/H3 Structure (pending — explicitly requested by Tiny)","path":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-11.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","u