n Tiny asked you to take notes, make a note, remember something, or similar directive. Search for these patterns:\n   - \"take notes\"\n   - \"make a note\"\n   - \"I want you to remember\"\n   - \"note this\"\n   - \"remember this\"\n   - \"don't forget\"\n   - Any explicit instruction to save something to a file\n\n3. For each finding, record:\n   - Date/time of the instruction\n   - What Tiny asked you to note\n   - Whether you actually noted it (yes/no/partial)\n   - If yes: which file it was saved to\n   - If no: why not (if discernible from context)\n\n4. Compile findings into a report at `memory/2026-03-27-note-compliance-audit.md` with:\n   - Summary stats (total instructions found, total complied, total missed)\n   - List of complied notes (with file locations)\n   - List of missed notes (with what was asked)\n   - Root cause analysis if patterns emerge\n\n5. ALSO: Using the same session files, find any feedback Tiny gave you that was NOT captured in any skills folder or memory file. This includes:\n   - Corrections\n   - Preferences stated\n   - Style critiques\n   - Rules he gave you\n\n6. Save any uncaptured feedback to `memory/2026-03-27-uncaptured-feedback.md`\n\nDo NOT draft content. Do NOT do any Nava work. Only audit, record, and report.\n\nWhen done, output a one-line summary: \"AUDIT COMPLETE: X note instructions found, Y complied, Z missed. Report at memory/2026-03-27-note-compliance-audit.md\""},"delivery":{"mode":"none","channel":"whatsapp","to":"+27763674298"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1775944800000,"lastRunAtMs":1775858400171,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":353590,"lastDelivered":false,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-delivered","consecutiveErrors":0}},{"id":"4ee0c18c-e191-402f-83c6-a551ed2850b2","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"Dream Mode — Nightly Reflection","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1775200564020,"updatedAtMs":1775859015243,"schedule":{"expr":"0 0 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Africa/Johannesburg"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"## Task: Dream Mode — Nightly Reflection\\n\\nYou are running an isolated reflection session. Your ONLY job:\n\\n1. Using the session-logs skill (read ~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/session-logs/SKILL.md first, use jq commands), find the session JSONL file for yesterday (2026-04-02).\\n\\n2. Extract from that session:\\n   - Key decisions made\\n   - Lessons learned\\n   - Things Tiny mentioned in passing (potential reminders)\\n   - Feedback/corrections from Tiny\\n   - Current project status updates\\n   - Any open TODOs or pending items\\n\\n3. Distill these into durable memories:\\n   - Write significant events/lessons/insights to memory/2026-04-02.md (yesterday's file)\\n   - Update MEMORY.md with anything worth keeping long-term\\n   - Note any patterns or recurring themes\\n\\n4. Prepare a brief for Tiny:\\n   - 3-5 bullet-point insights from yesterday's work\\n   - Any reminders that should be set for today\\n   - Status of any ongoing projects\\n\\n5. Do NOT:\\n   - Draft content for Nava or other projects\\n   - Make external changes\\n   - Interfere with the main session\\n\\nWhen done, output a one-line summary: \"DREAM MODE COMPLETE: Insights distilled to memory/2026-04-02.md and MEMORY.md updated.\""},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1775944800000,"lastRunAtMs":1775858753762,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":261481,"lastDelivered":false,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-delivered","consecutiveErrors":0}},{"id":"c71bb64e-9818-4753-9a1c-19139739732f","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"OneDrive Backup — Full restore kit","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774654744600,"updatedAtMs":1775865631995,"schedule":{"expr":"0 2 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Africa/Johannesburg"},"sessionTarget":"main","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"systemEvent","text":"OneDrive backup trigger — build full restore kit to C:\\Users\\Tiny4