as requested by the user.\n\n## Critical Context\nThe conversation was interrupted/prefixed. The user has two versions of the enforceability section (reference and new) and wants the assistant to identify the differences. The full file content was truncated in the display. The enforceability section needs to be located within the document to perform the comparison.\n\n<read-files>\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/awaa-output/phase-5-full-draft.md\n\n</read-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"326fb1bd","tokensBefore":99389,"details":{"readFiles":["/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/awaa-output/phase-5-full-draft.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
