{"type":"message","id":"8ddc6197","parentId":"43ebbe3b","timestamp":"2026-04-11T13:11:43.664Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Editor skill updated with:\n\n- **Principle 8** — Repetition → Evidence. When three sentences do the same job, replace the announcement with the specific content they were gesturing toward. MEAL Evidence step.\n- **Critical workflow flag** — Passes 1 and 2 marked non-negotiable.\n- **Analysis fix logged** — Missing causal link (financial dependence → reclassification) is the MEAL Analysis step AWAA skipped.\n\nReady for next H3."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":47081,"output":137,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47218,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775913103663}}
