 (leave it alone in this step)\n- The Bottom Line / conclusion (leave it alone in this step)\n- The opening story (leave it exactly as provided)","old_string":"**What NOT to touch:**\n- H2 and H3 headings (write around them, they stay as-is)\n- H2 intro paragraphs (leave them alone in this step)\n- The FAQ section (leave it alone in this step)\n- The Bottom Line / conclusion (leave it alone in this step)\n- The opening story (leave it exactly as provided)","file_path":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/drafting-skill/SKILL.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":49962,"output":562,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50524,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775913244805}}
